The code of this small project is to be regarded as 'Open-Source'

You may use this code as inspiration or even directly take smaller
snippets as long as you don't blatalantly copy the whole program
or significant amounts of it and pass it of as your own work.

If you think it is appropriate to give me credit feel free to do
so and link to my website https://www.eric-poehlsen.de or the
Github repository.